{
  "stem": "21786.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forgot to mention, the reason I gave to the Gestapo and to the SS why I want to join-- I had to proclaim Eva for my bri-- for-- for my bride, and I simply put her into a tender stant-- state of pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was pregnant with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why I considered it fair to join her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we moved, then, to this huge kind of waiting space where Eva was with her mother, and I was explaining how it came about that I am there, she really believed that Eva is pregnant with me.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she believed it literally until [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she, poor thing, went to the gas chambers, I think.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyhow, there we were, out of these barracks, and Eva was put into a building where-- where live the young women.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that point, one can say girls, for they had been about 15, 16, 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were about 16 together in one room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We mentioned the space.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were triple bunks, and they get along marvellously.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They all were Zionist kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was living at that point, for a relatively short time, in one of the main military barracks, where there were about 4,000 or 5,000 men living together, and we were in triple bunks in different sections of that huge building.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, I got myself out and about in, I would say, four to five months.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was working, at that point, in the agriculture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was simply we worked on the fields outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were cultivating cucumbers and tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The harvest, naturally, didn't belong to Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The harvest belonged to the SS man.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
